value.0: Oh, you be back! What can I, Ber Delanion, do for you good <master/mistress>? Is this a sign that the evil mistress, she who whips and beats me, maybe, she be dead?
Oh, please do. I am very nervous and am near to being a wreck, I am.
Oh that is so terrific. You are best hero ever, I do say so, indeed I do. Now I tell you what I know, I will.
Bessada Ne'Phaz was powerful cleric of Lloth, evil Spider Goddess. The other day she comes to the house of my mistress while I am serving her.
She say that drow army will go up to cave near surface and get young boy who be hiding there.
She did not say how she knew, she did not, even though my mistress did ask. She just said there would be a big reward.
So she gathered this army, because she is powerful as priestess and all of a sudden she is also sorceress too, so my mistress knows she speaks true about rewards.
We did find the boy where she said, indeed, and now she has him in caves past door. You need the key if you want to go past door, yes you will.
That is all I know, good <master/mistress>.
Svirfneblin will remember you with great fondness, we will. Good luck to you.
She is in the cave to the west of here, she is indeed.
Oh, what can you be wanting now?
Oh, sad goodbye.
Eeep! Oh, please don't kill me. Oh no, I am not your enemy, no I am not. I will be a help to you, just please do not kill me.
Eeek! Then me fight you if me must!
Oh, thank you kind <master/mistress>. I would most assuredly flee this place; I would indeed, except that I fear the mistress.
She would draw pictures on my body and carve my flesh as a sacrifice to her terrible Spider Goddess; oh, she surely would, I am certain! Would you be able to help me, maybe, kind <master/mistress>?
Oh, sad is this day, oh, yes, it is sad indeed.
Mistress has magic ability to find me; oh for certain, and so I need for you, strong, mighty one, to find and kill her, yes I do.
She has key, key that you might need to find the little boy that I am thinking you are finding, yes?
Oh, I was sure you here to save the child, I did think so, yes.
I will tell you about the poor child after you kill mistress, oh yes I will.
Oh, that is wonderful news, yes it is. Go quick into the next cavern and there she will be for you to kill. Bring me back the key to know she is dead.
Best of luck I wish you.
Oh, I do not have any gold, oh no. The mistress does not let me have gold, she doesn't. I have only information that I can pay you with.
Oh <sir/madam>, I am Ber Delanion, of the Delanion svirfneblin clan. I am the slave of a very mean drow; oh yes, I certainly am.
Oh, it would be a joy to help someone who won't tie me with chains and flay the skin from my body, oh, yes it would.
Oh, oh, oh, I would trade one cruelty for another would I? I should think not. I should think I will stay with cruelty known, I will.
She is terrible, cruel mistress, she is, she is. She has Spider Goddess to follow, but she also follows Bessada Ne'Phaz.
You not know Lloth? She be big, mean, nasty drow goddess. Me not like her, no not one little bit, I do not! Bessada is her priestess and a powerful one she is, yes indeed, she certainly is.
Bessada is the one who tells everyone else what to do, surely she is!
I tell you more if you help me, oh yes, so much more, but I need to be safe, yes safe.
Oh, I cannot do so. It would be very bad if I tell you and you don't help me, oh yes, it would.

Comment.value: Ber scared of PC. Should appear over his head and Drow should spawn in to attack PC.

value.0: Help, help, mistress! Intruder, murder, oh, help!
Me get to it soon.
I'm getting to it.
You mistress be dead and me get her key.
Your mistress is dead and I have her key.
Who tell her 'bout boy?
Who told her about this boy?
How she know Melorius be hid there?
How did she know Melorius would be there?
Okay, you go home now.
All right. I guess you can leave now.
There be other stuff you know?
Is there anything else you know?
Where be you mistress again?
Where is your mistress again?
Nothing. Goodbye.
What you be want 'gain?
Tell me what you want again.
Me no like begging. Me kill you now.
I don't like grovellers. Prepare to die.
You go or me kill you maybe?
Get out of here before I decide to kill you.
No, me no can bother help you. Get lost.
No, I don't have time to help you. Get lost.
Me could help you, maybe. What you want?
Well, I suppose maybe I could. What do you need?
What you mean boy? Me not know no boy.
What boy? What are you talking about?
You know where boy be?
You know where the boy is?
You tell me or me hurt you badder than you mistress do!
You tell me, or I'll hurt you worse than your mistress ever did.
No, me not do that.
No, I don't think I can do that.
Okay, me kill bad woman for you.
Okay, I'll kill her for you.
What you pay me to kill you mistress, huh?
What will you pay me to kill her?
What you do here?
What are you doing here?
Who you be? Why you be with drow?
Who are you? Why are you with these drow?
You be slave? You help me, maybe?
You're a slave? Perhaps you could help me?
Me not say me no hurt you too. You listen good, okay?
I never said I wouldn't do those things to you! You had better obey me.
You mistress be cruel. You tell me 'bout her, okay?
Your mistress sounds cruel. Why don't you begin by telling me about her?
Who be this Spider Goddess?
Who is the Spider Goddess?
Who be this Bess with big name?
Who is this Bessada Ne'Phaz?
You tell me 'bout stuff first, then me help you, maybe?
How about you tell me first and then I'll think about helping you?
Tell me stuff or me hurt you.
Tell me or I'll hurt you worse than your mistress ever has!
